<subSubSection id="C34472A7FFF86825459A3461B91AFE41" pageId="13" pageNumber="296" type="discussion">
<paragraph id="8BE1212CFFF86825459A3461B91AFE41" blockId="13.[151,1436,289,460]" pageId="13" pageNumber="296">
<emphasis id="B92AFD3EFFF86825459A3461BB40FE09" bold="true" box="[199,315,362,388]" pageId="13" pageNumber="296">Remarks.</emphasis>
<taxonomicName id="4C5E5AAFFFF86825441C3460BB87FE09" authorityName="Cartwright" authorityYear="1990" box="[321,508,362,388]" class="Insecta" family="Ecnomidae" genus="Ecnomus" kingdom="Animalia" order="Trichoptera" pageId="13" pageNumber="296" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="kitabal">
<emphasis id="B92AFD3EFFF86825441C3460BB87FE09" box="[321,508,362,388]" italics="true" pageId="13" pageNumber="296">Ecnomus kitabal</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
was previously recorded from northern NSW, eastern 
<collectingRegion id="499AEFCEFFF8682541043461BE9BFE09" box="[1113,1248,362,388]" country="Australia" name="Queensland" pageId="13" pageNumber="296">Queensland</collectingRegion>
, and one locality in northern WA, but until now without records from the NT (
<bibRefCitation id="EFCF5CDDFFF8682546603485B980FE25" author="Cartwright, D. I." box="[829,1019,398,424]" pageId="13" pageNumber="296" pagination="1 - 48" refId="ref14543" refString="Cartwright, D. I. (1990) The Australian species of Ecnomus McLachlan (Trichoptera: Ecnomidae). Memoirs of the Museum of Victoria, 51, 1 - 48. https: // doi. org / 10.24199 / j / mmv. 1990.51.01" type="journal article" year="1990">Cartwright 1990</bibRefCitation>
). The species is newly recorded from the NT with the addition of 
<specimenCount id="9D58EAA5FFF86825449234B9B83DFE41" box="[463,582,434,460]" pageId="13" pageNumber="296" type="male">four males</specimenCount>
collected from two sites.
</paragraph>
